ActsAsEncrypted
===============

Quick start:

 * gem install daemons

 * Get QuickCert here: http://segment7.net/projects/ruby/QuickCert/QuickCert-1.0.2.tar.gz
   Install with ruby setup.rb

*  Generate some keys in plugins/acts_as_encrypted/keys:
 
   $ cd plugins/acts_as_encrypted/keys
   $ vi qc_config
   [change passphrases etc]
   $ QuickCert
   [CA, server keys/certs and client certs generated]

 * Start server:

   $ cd plugins/acts_as_encrypted
   $ ./bin/server.rb run
   Enter PEM pass phrase: ****
   
 * Run test

   $ cd $RAILS_ROOT
   $ ruby vendor/plugins/acts_as_encrypted/test/acts_as_encrypted_test.rb
   Loaded suite vendor/plugins/acts_as_encrypted/test/acts_as_encrypted_test
   Started
   ...
 
